## Coordinator Agent
- Decomposes user requests into agent tasks
- Schedules agents asynchronously
- Orchestrates concurrent execution
- Aggregates results
- Handles execution errors

Example orchestration:
```python
results = await asyncio.gather(
    news_agent.run(),
    market_agent.run(),
    risk_agent.run(),
    strategy_agent.run()
)
```
This approach minimizes latency and keeps the research workflow responsive.

